{"tid":503889,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"施永青籲青年勿再埋怨：以後日子會更難過","createTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T05:05:49.000Z","uid":20058,"like":9,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":49,"replies":[{"pid":"42c04822aa884a573e6bdd499618390d83c046f8","tid":503889,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:35:02.000Z","msg":"中原集團主席施永青於《am730》專欄談及內地與香港形勢，指香港人在內地優勢已經減少，呼籲年輕人「不要再埋怨了，因為你們以後的日子會更難過」。<br />\n<br />\n專欄題為＜港人返大陸 已不吃香＞。施永青表示，香港廠商很多已沒法在內地有足夠競爭力，形容內地生態環境愈來愈不利港商，估計今後更多港商需要撤退。<br />\n<br />\n施永青以自己作例，指他到內地發展初期，先在港物色人手派上內地工作，惟漸漸發現內地員工進步很快，可勝任前線、管理級別及專業性質工作，且由於內地員工工資較低、有當地人脈關係、推理與演說能力比香港人優勝，故其內地公司已甚少聘用香港人。<br />\n<br />\n施永青之後談及香港年輕人，稱在香港找工作並不困難，「年輕人不滿的是待遇不夠好與升職機會少罷了」，惟他呼籲年輕人不要再埋怨，明言「因為你們以後的日子會更難過」。<br />\n<br />\n他解釋，當內地人知識、技能與鬥心都比得上香港時，香港工種會繼續流失，預期未來香港工作崗位會減少，工資水平也會下降，「我們沒法阻止別人在別處與我們競爭。這是所有發達地區今後都得面對的問題，香港不會例外」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171219/s00001/1513673832252\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171219%2Fs00001%2F1513673832252&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2Fppe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=494eb786\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171219%2Fs00001%2F1513673832252&h=8e7884bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171219/s00001/1513673832252</a>"},{"pid":"a30f4f5b2b6d5f2b9ae2dfae6e8c2d5bb13e1172","tid":503889,"uid":143499,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:40:54.000Z","msg":"樓主幾時寄聖誕卡俾屍永青<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a151a0beb9594bc98774ca11b9aed2c209a9ce22","tid":503889,"uid":57488,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:41:30.000Z","msg":"日子更難過同埋怨兩樣嘢<br />\n有咩關係<br />\n<br />\n望住班撚樣日日賣港去同大陸接軌<br />\n點解唔可以埋怨<br />\n反枱又話你激進<br />\n你班上曬神枱嘅仆街食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2633af89b4bf65c95a7a91d82927d6a17e02a2a","tid":503889,"uid":120123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:42:01.000Z","msg":"杏家産...."},{"pid":"cf6ef521fadf4fd1caa3bb5b640779c801f5e6b5","tid":503889,"uid":156327,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:45:38.000Z","msg":"連登要扺制中原嗎？"},{"pid":"dca910495953ff9493b0a03f29e9d4559d041819","tid":503889,"uid":26752,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T10:46:48.000Z","msg":"當初收聖誕卡個陣你又唔識咁諗既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d4361fe9b3b451d5f83bb15d359f439a84def3","tid":503889,"uid":60287,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:02:32.000Z","msg":"你係你班含家產搞到生活咁難過你個仆街仲好意思講"},{"pid":"46a4e69bb30da518cbd7dce578a5008a20f899a5","tid":503889,"uid":11001,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">施永青，聖誕快樂</span></span>"},{"pid":"dbae4fc26132ab52abd4effd2de61051f2071287","tid":503889,"uid":60287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:02:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就係你班含家產搞到生活咁難過你個仆街仲好意思講</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5989ae4d15ac6ea173bcd54a488e7158482a37ff","tid":503889,"uid":20058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:40:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"677c894618de89866670340af4efff6762e8d6ca","tid":503889,"uid":52595,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:44:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"634cc7e7d1b61ea3df1b2a72aa6ed20471019ce2","tid":503889,"uid":21917,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:45:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2Fppe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=8d5a61fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&h=f1ad1725\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997</a><br />\n每年聖誕都要幫施生重溫下"},{"pid":"c1b160eece3e7a81e7a9b1b5ffc3951db6f7a6a4","tid":503889,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:45:56.000Z","msg":"又黎香港人唔夠人競爭理論<br />\non99"},{"pid":"80b752f2ff30cbcd373a0bf0c6ac68bf6bcc961d","tid":503889,"uid":54959,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:47:10.000Z","msg":"呢班人賣港投共之後嘅香港梗係更難捱啦"},{"pid":"70861bd87f64ea48fac3943dc0783c778942d1c9","tid":503889,"uid":52595,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:47:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"406f2efcc40e590d3e710fe3e1f1c766ef2afbc4","tid":503889,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:49:35.000Z","msg":"李嘉誠沒競爭力 對中國沒什麼重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b216e5acab7979479168804894b0f3f0becb91a","tid":503889,"uid":635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:54:07.000Z","msg":"中原上到去大陸咪又係一舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5d57b0f356032306352873b6bb2daf5051d3164","tid":503889,"uid":48157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:54:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c662fde69c5fdb0e8ad82331d07aac8f40e5eb69","tid":503889,"uid":21917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2Fppe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=8d5a61fe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20121218%2F51189997&h=f1ad1725\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20121218/51189997</a><br />\n每年聖誕都要幫施生重溫下</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/19/194736_31be4737879dbdd2f9b4111ee442368b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F19%2F194736_31be4737879dbdd2f9b4111ee442368b.jpg&h=1d5722e6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n要電腦先睇到  唔知點整個手機LINK出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ababe4353b2088f8f8b281588d724e839ff8253","tid":503889,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:07:03.000Z","msg":"sbt<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7e466a10988596a0df2975735b499070ea11780","tid":503889,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:17:57.000Z","msg":"大家咁話啦"},{"pid":"3a3e84738901cbc2227c0ef31141b80d29d7a264","tid":503889,"uid":635,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>施永青間中原係支那俾人搶生意 就發爛渣寫文屌人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.am730.com.hk/column-267095 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.am730.com.hk%2Fcolumn-267095%20&d=B%2Bw2zJwXHmCdvCVYd%2B%2Fppe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=dec43864\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.am730.com.hk/column-267095 </a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我經營的地產代理行業，「有幸」被「互聯網人」看中，認為只要能夠借助互聯網解決這個行業的訊息不平衡狀態，就可以釋放大量生產力，並令消費者可以享用到更加「價廉物美」的服務。他們預期，傳統的經營者將很快的被顛覆，而不得不退出市場。 <br />\n<br />\n他們在未能降低營運成本的情況下，已向客戶降低收費，甚至完全免費。譬如最近就有一些公司竟完全不收租客與業主的佣金，而買賣也只收0.5%(內地的公價是共3%)。表面上，這好像對消費者很有利，但很明顯，商業機構不可能長期用貼錢的方式去運作，待他們清除競爭對手，壟斷市場後，消費者看到的將是另一種嘴臉。</blockquote><br />\n年輕人籲施永青勿再埋怨：以後日子會更難過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c04a03cfa208dd5cf7e81b729e85949f9290a5","tid":503889,"uid":52403,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:20:13.000Z","msg":"其實講得啱，當港樓泡爆之後，起碼會好似日本咁長達數十年經濟衰退。"},{"pid":"a1f301e907894aa0c4a6781c0ec295674fd2a67e","tid":503889,"uid":83251,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:21:24.000Z","msg":"因為地產狗日日炒地，所以先會愈黎愈難過"},{"pid":"2d78eda4768a32c5e0690a076c57c7405523f77f","tid":503889,"uid":604,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:43:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登要扺制中原嗎？</blockquote><br />\n你有幫襯開咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b259e4f84e5e37c54f73298783ea99684aec20f1","tid":503889,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d35cad7860244ea3bb259551327cb26615d3d9d5","tid":503889,"uid":40337,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T12:59:24.000Z","msg":"無講錯"},{"pid":"b47618298c6814e3f86ea14f452b2f7fba538b6e","tid":503889,"uid":75072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:00:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中原上到去大陸咪又係一舊屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不思進取 Q房果啲贏佢十條街"},{"pid":"6fccb10fea6f890aded3f9fcf0e733a4d143de8a","tid":503889,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:02:58.000Z","msg":"就到聖誕 屍生好大陰影 <br />\n又靠踩低青年擦存在感<br />\n但個個青年都瘋狂慶祝聖誕無人so佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"781ae2441f1ca4b0afee2469930ad3820da7a610","tid":503889,"uid":35814,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:08:43.000Z","msg":"離地到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問一個地方接受教育嘅人數多左<br />\n確實係整體競爭力會上升<br />\n亦唔排除真係有班人叻啲<br />\n<br />\n但社會個大環境<br />\n係官商勾結搞成咁<br />\n如果香港有心搞工業搞科研<br />\n工種增加<br />\n令大部份人讀書唔係只為一張沙紙<br />\n做到真正學以致用<br />\n而唔係一窩蜂咁走去炒股炒地炒樓<br />\n你估香港班後生會唔會冇競爭力？<br />\n自己有份搞到個社會咁仲有面講下一代唔掂<br />\n你條撚樣真係小心突然破產妻離子散身染絕症長命百歲呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d479d961a4c5a745be24cebf4ca0f0bc012024","tid":503889,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:18:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>就到聖誕 屍生好大陰影 <br />\n又靠踩低青年擦存在感<br />\n但個個青年都瘋狂慶祝聖誕無人so佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d680917c884d5a33902bb38c41a2a3d83c0d2066","tid":503889,"uid":126510,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:20:49.000Z","msg":"佢立論係黑人憎<br />\n但論據係合理既<br />\n<br />\n大陸同外邊接觸多咗 <br />\n港台人士喺大陸已經無咩技術或者資訊上既優勢<br />\n相反佢地作為本地人有好多著數<br />\n有同學所以各行各業都有人脈 ，明白國情知道內地人情世故 <br />\n人工又低，你好難同佢爭<br />\n<br />\n以前政策上好多優惠畀港台人士吸納資金同技術<br />\n而家反而只會打壓你，尤其係做製造業加工業或者低技術個班<br />\n佢地自己人都做到，點解要益你？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好再宣傳叫香港人返大陸創業或者做野啦唔該<br />\n根本唔L work"},{"pid":"d8acd8900ad86dffb6949e4e33d19f09bcac4127","tid":503889,"uid":127244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-19T13:21:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>離地到上太空<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n毫無疑問一個地方接受教育嘅人數多左<br />\n確實係整體競爭力